<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.6.6">
<l>pēyirukku neṭuveḷḷam peruvicumpiṉ mītōṭip perukukālam</l>
<l>tāyirukkum vaṇṇamē yummaittaṉ vayiṟṟirutti yuyyakkoṇṭāṉ</l>
<l>pōyirukka maṟṟiṅkōr pututteyvaṅ koṇṭāṭun toṇṭīrpeṟṟa</l>
<l>tāyirukka maṇaivennīrāṭ ṭutirōmāṭ ṭātataka vaṟṟīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You devotees who celebrate another new deity here</l>
<l rend="indent">when you have left the one</l>
<l>Who took you to save [you], placing you in his belly in the way of a mother,</l>
<l>At the time when a vast flood, where [only] spirits lived, swelled,</l>
<l rend="indent">spreading over the great heavens,</l>
<l>Would you bathe the [birthing] stool in warm water</l>
<l rend="indent">since a mother who birthed [a child] sat [there],</l>
<l rend="indent">you who are without morality which is not [within your] ability?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
